MASTER FLOW (SIMPLIFIED OVERVIEW)
Client Onboard → Request Upload → Vendor Audit → Sealed Bid → Open Auction → Finalization → Payment → Pickup → Compliance
________________________________________
🔷 1. ONBOARDING FLOW (MANUAL APPROVAL)
🏢 Client Onboarding
Flow:
1.	Client registers on portal 
2.	Admin reviews details 
3.	Admin approves manually 
👉 Status: Client Approved
________________________________________
🚛 Vendor Onboarding
Flow:
1.	Vendor registers 
2.	Upload: 
o	License 
o	GST 
o	Pollution Certificate 
3.	Admin approves manually 
👉 Status: Vendor Approved
________________________________________
🔷 2. CLIENT REQUIREMENT UPLOAD FLOW
📊 Step 1: Bulk Upload
•	Client uploads product list (Excel) 
📊 Step 2: Internal Processing (We Connect)
•	Clean & standardize sheet 
•	Add: 
o	Categories 
o	Estimated weight 
o	Base format 
📊 Step 3: Client Approval
•	Updated sheet shared on portal 
•	Client confirms: 
o	Product list 
o	Target price 
👉 Status: Requirement Finalized
________________________________________
🔷 3. VENDOR AUDIT FLOW
📩 Step 4: Audit Invitation
Two options:
Option A (Recommended)
•	Vendors get email + portal notification 
•	Click → View audit details on portal 
Option B
•	Accept/Reject via email (basic version) 
👉 Status: Audit Invited
________________________________________
✅ Step 5: Vendor Accept / Reject
•	Vendor clicks: 
o	Accept 
o	Reject 
👉 Status:
•	Accepted → Audit Scheduled 
•	Rejected → ignore 
________________________________________
📍 Step 6: SPOC Sharing
•	After acceptance: 
o	Vendor sees: 
	Site address 
	SPOC contact 
👉 Auto email triggered
________________________________________
📝 Step 7: Audit Completion
Vendor updates on portal:
•	Product match? 
o	✅ Yes 
o	❌ No (with remarks) 
👉 Status: Audit Completed
________________________________________
🔷 4. SEALED BID FLOW
🔒 Step 8: Sealed Bid Creation
•	Admin creates sealed bid event 
📩 Step 9: Vendor Notification
•	Email + portal alert 
________________________________________
💰 Step 10: Vendor Submission
Vendor uploads:
•	Price sheet (Excel) 
•	Remarks (comment box) 
👉 Status: Sealed Bid Submitted
________________________________________
🧠 Step 11: Internal Review
•	We Connect reviews all bids 
•	Shortlist vendors 
👉 Suggestion:
👉 Add auto comparison table (best price highlight)
________________________________________
📤 Step 12: Share with Client
•	Client views bids on portal 
👉 Status: Client Review
________________________________________
🔷 5. OPEN BID (AUCTION FLOW)
⚙️ Step 13: Auction Setup
Client + Admin defines:
•	Base Price → Client 
•	Target Price → Client 
•	Tick Size → Admin 
•	Max Tick → Admin 
•	Extension Time → Admin 
•	Start/End Time → Client 
👉 Status: Auction Scheduled
________________________________________
🔥 Step 14: Live Auction
•	Vendors bid in real-time 
•	Rank visible 
•	Auto extension (last 3 mins rule) 
👉 Status: Auction Live
________________________________________
🥇 Step 15: Winner Selection
•	Rank 1 vendor selected 
👉 Status: Vendor Finalized
________________________________________
🔷 6. FINAL QUOTE & CLIENT APPROVAL
📄 Step 16: Final Submission
Vendor uploads:
•	Final product-wise quote 
•	Letterhead quotation 
________________________________________
📤 Step 17: Client Approval
•	Client reviews final quote 
•	Approves 
👉 Status: Deal Closed
________________________________________
🔷 7. PAYMENT FLOW
💳 Step 18: Invoice Flow
•	Vendor pays: 
o	Client amount 
o	5% commission to We Connect 
👉 Both account details shown on portal
________________________________________
📤 Step 19: Payment Proof Upload
•	Vendor uploads: 
o	Payment screenshot / UTR 
👉 Status: Payment Submitted
________________________________________
✅ Step 20: Payment Approval
•	Admin verifies 
👉 Status: Payment Confirmed
________________________________________
🔷 8. PICKUP & COMPLIANCE FLOW
🚛 Step 21: Pickup Arrangement
•	Vendor schedules pickup 
________________________________________
📋 Step 22: Pickup Day Submission
Vendor uploads:
•	Form 6 
•	Weight Slip: 
o	Empty vehicle 
o	Loaded vehicle 
________________________________________
📜 Step 23: Compliance Documents
Vendor uploads:
•	Recycling Certificate 
•	Disposal Certificate 
________________________________________
✅ Step 24: Admin Approval
•	We Connect verifies 
________________________________________
📥 Step 25: Client Access
•	Client can: 
o	Download all documents 
👉 Status: Completed
________________________________________
🔷 9. FINAL STATUS FLOW
Onboarded → Requirement Finalized → Audit → Sealed Bid → Auction → Finalized → Payment → Pickup → Completed
________________________________________
